snippet.textDisplay: Although the actions recommended seem to be relevant, the fast and loose use of the terms "epidemic" and "pandemic" is irresponsible. snippet.textDisplay:
Finally! Some people talking sense about this novel virus. I’m not panicking, just preparing. There’s a difference. My biggest concern is that hospitals like mine are not even able to test for this strain. It’s flu season.
